Agile methodology has come a long way to become a  popular approach among a wide variety of organisation.it is a method of project management where projects are organised into epics then broken down into small managable section via chapters and sprints .while this method is often associated with software development and devops ,it has a wide range of application through out the business
popular software on agile:-Atlassian jira,Agilean ,Sprint Ground,Version one,Spira team.
why agile project management is right choice:1.faster lead time,2.a reduction in adminstrative procedure 3.Reduction in the risk of project failure4.regular incremental delivery of product.
